ya abhyantara suji"}, {"start": 687.5, "end": 689.5, "text": " one becomes completely"}, {"start": 689.5, "end": 691.5, "text": " purified externally and internally"}, {"start": 691.5, "end": 693.5, "text": " by simply remembering the lotus"}, {"start": 693.5, "end": 695.5, "text": " side supreme god"}, {"start": 695.5, "end": 697.5, "text": " so how do we remember the lotus side supreme god"}, {"start": 697.5, "end": 699.5, "text": " by chanting Hare Krishna"}, {"start": 699.5, "end": 701.5, "text": " so Srila Prabhupada taught us"}, {"start": 701.5, "end": 703.5, "text": " to chant Hare Krishna"}, {"start": 703.5, "end": 705.5, "text": " and thereby purify"}, {"start": 705.5, "end": 707.5, "text": " ourselves"}, {"start": 707.5, "end": 709.5, "text": " and be fit"}, {"start": 709.5, "end": 711.5, "text": " for serving Krishna"}, {"start": 711.5, "end": 713.5, "text": " for doing Deity worship"}, {"start": 713.5, "end": 715.5, "text": " like this"}, {"start": 715.5, "end": 717.5, "text": " Prabhupada has given"}, {"start": 717.5, "end": 719.5, "text": " the"}, {"start": 719.5, "end": 721.5, "text": " the essential"}, {"start": 721.5, "end": 723.5, "text": " principles"}, {"start": 723.5, "end": 725.5, "text": " so that we can"}, {"start": 725.5, "end": 727.5, "text": " execute the"}, {"start": 727.5, "end": 729.5, "text": " follow those principles"}, {"start": 729.5, "end": 731.5, "text": " and achieve the purpose"}, {"start": 731.5, "end": 733.5, "text": " of"}, {"start": 733.5, "end": 735.5, "text": " properly"}, {"start": 735.5, "end": 737.5, "text": " practicing"}, {"start": 737.5, "end": 739.5, "text": " the"}, {"start": 739.5, "end": 741.5, "text": " religious principles"}, {"start": 741.5, "end": 743.5, "text": " to make advancement in Krishna"}, {"start": 743.5, "end": 745.5, "text": " consciousness to achieve perfection"}, {"start": 745.5, "end": 747.5, "text": " of"}, {"start": 747.5, "end": 749.5, "text": " purifying ourselves"}, {"start": 749.5, "end": 751.5, "text": " completely of all material contamination"}, {"start": 751.5, "end": 753.5, "text": " and going back to god"}, {"start": 753.5, "end": 755.5, "text": " so"}, {"start": 755.5, "end": 757.5, "text": " it is said here Bhishma Deva"}, {"start": 757.5, "end": 759.5, "text": " he is one of the"}, {"start": 759.5, "end": 761.5, "text": " twelve great authorities"}, {"start": 761.5, "end": 763.5, "text": " mahajanas"}, {"start": 763.5, "end": 765.5, "text": " twelve mahajanas"}, {"start": 765.5, "end": 767.5, "text": " svayambhu narada shambhu"}, {"start": 767.5, "end": 769.5, "text": " kumaran kapilao manubhu"}, {"start": 769.5, "end": 771.5, "text": " praladha janaka bheeshma"}, {"start": 771.5, "end": 773.5, "text": " valir vayasakhi vayam"}, {"start": 773.5, "end": 775.5, "text": " this verse"}, {"start": 775.5, "end": 777.5, "text": " in the sixth canton"}, {"start": 777.5, "end": 779.5, "text": " of the Bhagavatam"}, {"start": 779.5, "end": 781.5, "text": " is spoken by Yamaraj"}, {"start": 781.5, "end": 783.5, "text": " Yamarajis describe the twelve"}, {"start": 783.5, "end": 785.5, "text": " mahajanas"}, {"start": 785.5, "end": 787.5, "text": " Yamaraj is one of them"}, {"start": 787.5, "end": 789.5, "text": " Bhishma Deva is also"}, {"start": 789.5, "end": 791.5, "text": " one of the twelve mahajanas"}, {"start": 791.5, "end": 793.5, "text": " so he perfectly knew"}, {"start": 793.5, "end": 795.5, "text": " all the religious"}, {"start": 795.5, "end": 797.5, "text": " principles and he could make adjustments"}, {"start": 797.5, "end": 799.5, "text": " according to time and place"}, {"start": 799.5, "end": 801.5, "text": " so therefore he could receive and welcome"}, {"start": 801.5, "end": 803.5, "text": " all the powerful sages"}, {"start": 803.5, "end": 805.5, "text": " assembled there at his"}, {"start": 805.5, "end": 807.5, "text": " death bed from all parts of the"}, {"start": 807.5, "end": 809.5, "text": " universe"}, {"start": 809.5, "end": 811.5, "text": " now one special thing about Bhishma"}, {"start": 811.5, "end": 813.5, "text": " is"}, {"start": 813.5, "end": 815.5, "text": " he had a"}, {"start": 815.5, "end": 817.5, "text": " a benediction"}, {"start": 817.5, "end": 819.5, "text": " from his father"}, {"start": 819.5, "end": 821.5, "text": " that he could quit the body"}, {"start": 821.5, "end": 823.5, "text": " whenever he desired to"}, {"start": 823.5, "end": 825.5, "text": " by choosing an auspicious moment"}, {"start": 825.5, "end": 827.5, "text": " that's the sense in which"}, {"start": 827.5, "end": 829.5, "text": " that particular benediction"}, {"start": 829.5, "end": 831.5, "text": " was used"}, {"start": 831.5, "end": 833.5, "text": " because in the eighth chapter of the Bhagavatam"}, {"start": 833.5, "end": 835.5, "text": " Bhishma describes"}, {"start": 835.5, "end": 837.5, "text": " different auspicious and inauspicious"}, {"start": 837.5, "end": 839.5, "text": " times"}, {"start": 839.5, "end": 841.5, "text": " which"}, {"start": 841.5, "end": 843.5, "text": " are"}, {"start": 843.5, "end": 845.5, "text": " applicable for quitting the body"}, {"start": 845.5, "end": 847.5, "text": " if somebody quits"}, {"start": 847.5, "end": 849.5, "text": " the body at an auspicious time"}, {"start": 849.5, "end": 851.5, "text": " they are able to get out"}, {"start": 851.5, "end": 853.5, "text": " of this material existence and get"}, {"start": 853.5, "end": 855.5, "text": " liberation"}, {"start": 855.5, "end": 857.5, "text": " beyond this material"}, {"start": 857.5, "end": 859.5, "text": " existence"}, {"start": 859.5, "end": 861.5, "text": " if they quit at an inauspicious"}, {"start": 861.5, "end": 863.5, "text": " time then they cannot"}, {"start": 863.5, "end": 865.5, "text": " go out of this material"}, {"start": 865.5, "end": 867.5, "text": " world"}, {"start": 867.5, "end": 869.5, "text": " letting rebirth again"}, {"start": 871.5, "end": 873.5, "text": " but that is only applicable"}, {"start": 873.5, "end": 875.5, "text": " to non-devotees"}, {"start": 875.5, "end": 877.5, "text": " why? because devotees"}, {"start": 877.5, "end": 879.5, "text": " whenever they quit their body"}, {"start": 879.5, "end": 881.5, "text": " it doesn't matter"}, {"start": 881.5, "end": 883.5, "text": " because they are Krishna conscious"}, {"start": 883.5, "end": 885.5, "text": " whenever they quit their body"}, {"start": 885.5, "end": 887.5, "text": " they are definitely going"}, {"start": 887.5, "end": 889.5, "text": " back to Godhead"}, {"start": 889.5, "end": 891.5, "text": " they are getting ultimate liberation"}, {"start": 891.5, "end": 893.5, "text": " whenever they quit their body"}, {"start": 893.5, "end": 895.5, "text": " wherever they quit their body"}, {"start": 895.5, "end": 897.5, "text": " it doesn't matter time and place"}, {"start": 897.5, "end": 899.5, "text": " it doesn't matter for the devotees"}, {"start": 899.5, "end": 901.5, "text": " so Bhishma Deva as a pure devotee"}, {"start": 903.5, "end": 905.5, "text": " he need not choose an auspicious"}, {"start": 905.5, "end": 907.5, "text": " time for quitting the body"}, {"start": 907.5, "end": 909.5, "text": " neither he has to"}, {"start": 909.5, "end": 911.5, "text": " choose an auspicious place"}, {"start": 911.5, "end": 913.5, "text": " because"}, {"start": 913.5, "end": 915.5, "text": " he is a pure devotee"}, {"start": 915.5, "end": 917.5, "text": " he is guaranteed to go back to Godhead"}, {"start": 917.5, "end": 919.5, "text": " he is already liberated"}, {"start": 919.5, "end": 921.5, "text": " because he is a pure devotee"}, {"start": 921.5, "end": 923.5, "text": " but still"}, {"start": 923.5, "end": 925.5, "text": " in order to teach others"}, {"start": 925.5, "end": 927.5, "text": " because he was an expert"}, {"start": 927.5, "end": 929.5, "text": " yogi"}, {"start": 929.5, "end": 931.5, "text": " so he was"}, {"start": 931.5, "end": 933.5, "text": " waiting for the"}, {"start": 933.5, "end": 935.5, "text": " most auspicious moment"}, {"start": 935.5, "end": 937.5, "text": " to quit his body"}, {"start": 937.5, "end": 939.5, "text": " and the great sages knew"}, {"start": 939.5, "end": 941.5, "text": " that Bhishma is"}, {"start": 941.5, "end": 943.5, "text": " an authority in"}, {"start": 943.5, "end": 945.5, "text": " Dharma"}, {"start": 945.5, "end": 947.5, "text": " so they all assembled"}, {"start": 947.5, "end": 949.5, "text": " to witness Bhishma"}, {"start": 949.5, "end": 951.5, "text": " quitting his body"}, {"start": 951.5, "end": 953.5, "text": " at the most auspicious time"}, {"start": 953.5, "end": 955.5, "text": " Uttarayana Punyakala"}, {"start": 959.5, "end": 961.5, "text": " but Bhagavatam also"}, {"start": 961.5, "end": 963.5, "text": " describes in this very chapter"}, {"start": 963.5, "end": 965.5, "text": " that"}, {"start": 965.5, "end": 967.5, "text": " Bhishma Deva"}, {"start": 967.5, "end": 969.5, "text": " he"}, {"start": 969.5, "end": 971.5, "text": " quit his body"}, {"start": 971.5, "end": 973.5, "text": " in the presence of Krishna"}, {"start": 973.5, "end": 975.5, "text": " glorifying Krishna"}, {"start": 975.5, "end": 977.5, "text": " fixing his complete attention"}, {"start": 977.5, "end": 979.5, "text": " on Krishna"}, {"start": 979.5, "end": 981.5, "text": " at the time of his death"}, {"start": 981.5, "end": 983.5, "text": " so both ways"}, {"start": 983.5, "end": 985.5, "text": " Bhishma Deva was successful"}, {"start": 985.5, "end": 987.5, "text": " in quitting his body"}, {"start": 987.5, "end": 989.5, "text": " to attain ultimate liberation"}, {"start": 989.5, "end": 991.5, "text": " I will stop here"}, {"start": 991.5, "end": 993.5, "text": " Thank you very much"}]}